version_description: Close to what Weezer plays in their cover. Use bar chords for most.
Added the correct chords to the Bridge section, added in repeats, adjusted the placement of the chords to better fit the song's syllabic rhythm.
Acoustic version with capo allowing open chords instead of barre chords.

Version 1 is fine, its correct, but this is more correct. added transient chords, added missing chords during Solo section, corrected chord progression at end of chorus, adjusted the chords to fit over the exact lyric they are strummed, removed misplaced commentary, in general - its cleaner, more precise, with more chordal detail within the progression.
